          </h2>
          <p class="mx-auto max-w-xl text-zinc-400">
            The v1 release covers the real storefront surface: catalog, account, search, B2B, merchandising, and release packaging.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
